(firstQuint)Efficacy Of Itraconazole In Chronic Cavitary Pulmonary Aspergillosis.

 The role of itraconazole is still not clear in the treatment of chronic cavitary pulmonary aspergillosis(CCPA).

 Some studies have shown a beneficial role of itraconazole in reducing hemoptysis.

 So the present study is aimed at analyzing the role of itraconazole in CCPA.

